*hoe-1.8.0 (14 Oct 2008)

  14 Oct 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +hoe-1.8.0.ebuild:
  Version bump with 5 minor enhancements.

  03 Sep 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> hoe-1.7.0.ebuild:
  Depend on rubygems 1.2.0 since the generated tasks depend on it. Thanks to
  Cyril Mougel for providing the information in #236444.

  08 Jul 2008; Javier Villavicencio <the_paya@gentoo.org> hoe-1.7.0.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd.

  07 Jul 2008; Friedrich Oslage <bluebird@gentoo.org> hoe-1.7.0.ebuild:
  Add ~sparc keyword, bug #230517

*hoe-1.7.0 (01 Jul 2008)

  01 Jul 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +hoe-1.7.0.ebuild:
  Version bump with 3 minor enhancements:
    * Use rdoc 2.x gem if available. Eric likes his backslashes.
    * Added extra_dev_deps for new rubygems developer dependencies.
    * Finally got a sane test that does something. Hey... it's a start.

